There is an [unsafe default constructor defined ](
https://github.com/cocos2d/cocos2d-x/blob/bf35e0f6b57c627d871d9f3cbbe7a7dcf17505fe/cocos/math/Mat4.cpp#L32)for Mat4:
```.cpp
Mat4::Mat4()
{
    *this = IDENTITY;
}
```
If we declare some global Mat4 variable it may be initialized before IDENTITY will be.
So we'll get Mat4 initialized with invalid data.
